Hayward’s Vallares Sees Dana Gas as Possible Bid Target, FT Says

-- B y   N a m i t h a   J a g a d e e s h
-- 
2011-07-28T00:27:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/hayward-s-vallares-sees-dana-gas-as-possible-bid-target-ft-says.html
Vallares Plc, the investment company
backed by former BP Plc Chief Executive Officer  Tony Hayward ,
may consider bidding for  Dana Gas PJSC (DANA) , the Financial Times
reported, citing unnamed people familiar with the matter.  Representatives of both companies have met in recent months
and Vallares may be interested in Dana’s upstream gas assets in
Egypt and Kurdistan, the FT said without attribution.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Namitha Jagadeesh in London at 
 njagadeesh@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
